snippet.title: Qbics Paint Trailer for Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Your Nintendo Switch is about to fill up with creativity, art, fun – and the cutest voxel models you have ever seen! 

Qbics Paint, a game to put 3D modeling and painting at your fingertips, will be released for Nintendo Switch on July 27th for 4,99€.
